result.formatted_address: 3/F, 22 Yee Wo St, Causeway Bay, Hong Kong
result.name: Sawali Club Causeway Bay

reviews.text:
Food was subpar - The so-called Thai style hainanese chicken rice as cold and average in taste. Not even close to the real deal. 
The waiting period was the worst. Aside from the chicken rice, our fried rice and dishes came more than 30mins later, and far apart from each other. So you're basically finishing one dish at a time.

I enjoyed my dinner here. Lovely choice of salads, green curry tasted like in Thailand. Price was very reasonable, Chang beer as cold as you ex's heart. Environment so so, but service was top par!. Definitely a place to recommend for a friend.
One of the best Thai restaurants in HK
Service is great. Food is mediocre.
Fine Thai Reataurant

result.formatted_address: 3/F, 22 Yee Wo St, Causeway Bay, 香港
result.name: 金蘭花 銅鑼灣

reviews.text: 菜品貴但沒什麼質素可言，職員也是懶理客人，好像不消費多就是瘟神一樣
食品還可以，只是空調方面需要改善，大門營業時間大關，沒有風閘空調常流失，坐近門口附近坐位就會有點熱。
食品非常出色、環境優雅、服務態度非常好，五星評價，不會讓你失望！！推薦豬仔肉串燒、咖哩蟹、冬陰公！！
